text: Sekou Macalou (born 20 April 1995) is a French rugby union flanker who currently plays for Stade Français in the Top 14 and France. ==References== ==External links== *France profile at FFR *L'Équipe profile Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:French rugby union players Category:Stade Français rugby players Category:Rugby union flankers Category:France international rugby union players
